channel.title: Could Someone Please Help Me Find A Default Female Model?
channel.description:
Forgive me if I'm posting this in the wrong section, first time posting...Ever!
So I'm really trying to find a female/male default model so I can then convert it into a obj/3Ds/MQO so I can then use them for animation, as I have no idea how to create 3D models myself. I found a cache up to 6/12 and was able to find the hair IDs and Clothe IDs. But no actual default Male/Female characters. Could someone find me the model ID or maybe a .dat file or any kind of file for the default characters? Preferably 508+. Thank you in advance.
